data.description: Great opportunity to own a home in Southfield for under $300k. Recently updated kitchen & bathrooms (2015). New entry & security doors. Replacement windows throughout. 35 yr warranty on the windows. Monitored alarm system. Huge master suite with a walk-in closet & newly updated bathroom. Natural hardwood flooring throughout. Custom tile flooring in the kitchen. Updated hardwood flooring in the master bedroom. New hot water tank & furnace. Leaf filter gutter system recently added. New garage door. A fresh coat of paint makes everything like new.
